  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "640a04b4e5d8c0001b3c16ce",
      "text": "ChatGPTが読書感想文を書く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e0000548321",
      "text": "from [未踏ジュニアとLLM]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e0000548323",
      "text": "https://twitter.com/zikatu1/status/1631803964470759424",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e0000548324",
      "text": ">小5女子が自学で読書感想文を書いてきたんだけど、あまりにも上手すぎたので、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e0000548325",
      "text": "> 「もしかして、お母さんに手伝ってもらった？」と聞くと、「ううん、ちがうよ。これChatGPTが書いたの」と言われ驚いた。今年から作文コンクールはAIだらけになるかもしれない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e0000548326",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e0000548327",
      "text": "> 教室で話題になったので、次のような授業をしました",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e0000548328",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e0000548329",
      "text": "> ①作文を書く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e000054832a",
      "text": "> ②ChatGPTで添削する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e000054832b",
      "text": "> ③読み比べる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e000054832c",
      "text": "> ④変更点の理由をAIに教えてもらう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e000054832d",
      "text": "> ⑤学んだことをノートにまとめる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e000054832e",
      "text": "> ⑥AIが出せない味を話し合う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e000054832f",
      "text": "> ⑦使える部分を加え、修正する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e0000548330",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
    {
      "id": "640a04b4aff09e0000548331",
      "text": "> AIをどう使うか、どこで使うかを子供たちと共に学んでいきたい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678378165,
      "updated": 1678378165
    },
